t ms,geneva; font-size: large;\"><strong>7. Grace Potter </strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: trebuchet ms,geneva; font-size: large;\">With a voice like that of Jefferson Airplane front woman, Grace Slick, and an incredibly transcendent stage presence, Grace Potter from Grace Potter &amp; The Nocturnals is a 10 &ndash; to say the least. She is single-handedly changing the image of the free spirited hippie chick, and I thank her for that because it&rsquo;s about time.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-family: trebuchet ms,geneva;\">See more: </span><a href=\"http://www.gracepotter.com/photos\">http://www.gracepotter.com/photo</a></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: trebuchet ms,geneva; font-size: large;\">Hear more: <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oHlhOgQ36m8\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oHlhOgQ36m8</a></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: trebuchet ms,geneva; font-size: large;\"><strong>6. Jennifer Lawrence </strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: trebuchet ms,geneva; font-size: large;\"><em>Winter&rsquo;s Bone</em> was a great, albeit intense, movie and Jennifer looked decent enough throughout. However, when I saw her in her red dress at the Academy Awards (At age 20, she is officially the second youngest actress to be nominated for the award&hellip; pretty legit), I was BLOWN AWAY. I seriously couldn&rsquo;t believe she was the same girl from the film. Fortunately, thanks to the fact that she is an incredibly talented actress I think it&rsquo;s safe to say we&rsquo;ll be seeing more from the Kentucky-born smoke show.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-family: trebuchet m