=\"#000000\" /><param name=\"flashvars\" value=\"url=http://www.askmen.com/api/api_videos/config/slug:888-six-pack-abs-workout/embed:1\" /></object></span>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"amVideoEmbed\" class=\"amVideoEmbed\" style=\"width: 420px;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"http://askmen.com//video/sports/888-six-pack-abs-workout.html\">Get Six-Pack Abs With No Crunches</a></span></div>\r\n<div class=\"amVideoEmbed\" style=\"width: 420px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">e.b.k. lives, plays and dates in new york. if you have an eight-pack and those awesome handle-things on your hips, she\'ll be impressed and then make you a sandwich.</span></strong></div>','supertrainerrick','2012-01-09 16:47:14','2012-01-30 16:42:40',4,'8sixpack.jpg','image/jpeg',47969,'2012-01-09 16:47:13',0,'2012-01-30 16:42:40',1,'sixstepsixpack','sixstepsixpack'),(207,'Grilled Cheese, Two Ways','<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">We&rsquo;re hungry. We&rsquo;re lazy. We&rsquo;re into instant gratification.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">That adds up to an easy-peasy grilled cheese: A couple slices of bread, some (duh) cheese, and a bit of grease so it won&rsquo;t stick to our pan.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Presto snacko, right?</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Apparently not.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">We were shocked and ashamed of our peasant palates (meh, not so much) when we discovered what <a href=\"http://www.amateurgourmet.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Amateur Gourmet</a> was up to in his kitchen.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Slapping together what we thought was a seemingly simple sandwich was dragged out into a 12-shot instructional photo montage, complete with a detailed account of his snooty ingredient-procuring shopping spree.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">We&rsquo;re talking canvassing the streets for artisanal bread, farmers&rsquo; market honey, bleu cheese, white cheddar cheese, and countless other fresh ingredients. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">From a labor perspective, timing is everything: be sure to take out your butter from the fridge with enough time to bring it to room temperature. By the way, did you properly caramelize your onions? Tsk.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">How exhausting, and way to tarnish our childhood memories, pal.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">We proudly offer the rival ConnectingSexes version:</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Take two pieces of Wonder Bread from bag.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Wipe each side with butter.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Take a slice of Kraft cheese out of plastic; two, if you&rsquo;re spoiling yourself.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Put on one side of bread.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Cover with other slice of bread.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Put pan on stove.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Turn on burner, put pat of butter in pan.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">When you hear that sizzling sound, put sandwich into pan.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Before you smell that burnt smell, flip.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Before you smell that burnt smell, remove and put onto plate (optional).</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Eat.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Repeat if necessary.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">If not, be sure to TURN OFF STOVE.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">For the snobby Fancy Bread With Expensive Cheese and Other Items That Require Too Much Effort to Prepare, click here:</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"http://bit.ly/xlb1q2\">http://bit.ly/xlb1q2</a></span></p>','tipsandtricks','2012-01-09 18:27:34','2012-01-09 21:57:15',7,'8tips.jpg','image/jpeg',304067,'2012-01-09 18:27:33',0,'2012-01-09 21:57:15',1,'grilledcheese','grilledcheese'),(209,'Group Dating: It\'s Here','<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">As you know, I am a huge fan of blind dates. Whether I leave with a war story, a new friend or a potential boo-boo bear, it&rsquo;s always a worthwhile experience.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Not to sound like a greedy little girl, but let&rsquo;s cut to the straight dope:</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Having one stranger to think about is fun. Having five is fireworks.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">So what&rsquo;s my M.O.?</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Parties and networking events. They are like shooting fish in a barrel. I go out for one night, and leave having given my coordinates to many.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">I don&rsquo;t know how jammed your schedule is, but I only have so many hours in a week.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">How fabulous to use my precious time to work a room and talk with a multitude of potential one-on-ones, versus spending an evening focusing on JUST one dude.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Not to be crude, but when I think of the effort I have gone through for some dates, it&rsquo;s definitely been the law of diminishing returns when they&rsquo;ve turned out to be a waste of my time. &ldquo;I got all fancy for THIS?!&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">When I throw on my very best and bring the A-game for what works out to be a room filled with mini-dates, and then whittle those down to, call it four, real dates, I am happy I bothered&mdash;totally worth it.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">I cast a wider dating