helped by massage because stretching can\'t get into the nooks and crannies.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Still need to get sold on massage? Here are a few more of its amazing benefits:</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">It may help alleviate lower-back pain, and improve lower-back mobility.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">As far as performance goes, there is no better combination than stretching plus massage. The two together can help athletes recover from strenuous games and workouts.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">It may help promote tissue regeneration and the reduction of&nbsp;scar tissue.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">It may help exercise and stretch weak, tight, or atrophied muscles.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">It may release endorphins and amino acids that work as the body\'s natural painkiller.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">It may help&nbsp;ease pain medication dependence.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">It may help reduce spasms and cramping.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"> It may help relieve migraine pain by pumping oxygen and nutrients to tissues and vital organs, improving circulation.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">It may improve the condition of the body&rsquo;s largest organ&mdash;the skin.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Get the point? Get a massage.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br /></span></p>','supertrainerrick','2012-04-10 13:16:34','2012-04-10 13:25:22',4,'11fit2date.jpg','image/jpeg',15196,'2012-04-10 13:16:34',0,'2012-04-10 13:25:22',1,'massage','massage'),(269,'Destination Cufflinks','<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Buds blossoming on the trees, tulips pushing through the earth, and the chirps of little birds in the early morn.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">That&r